      "project_overview": "Eldeco 7 Peaks Residences is a premium 3 & 4 BHK oxy-rich residential project in Eldeco Greater Omicron 1 Greater Noida, thoughtfully planned across 7.5 acres of low-density green development. Featuring 7 standalone towers, wraparound balconies, abundant natural light, and resort-style amenities, this ultra-luxury address offers spacious layouts, privacy, and seamless connectivity to Yamuna Expressway, Noida Expressway, and the upcoming Noida International Airport—making it an ideal choice for both end-users and investors in Greater Noida.\r\n",
      "total_land": "6.5 Acres",
