      "video_review_text": "We will suggest you to buy this project ",
      "price_list_desc": "<p>Basic Sale Price of Eldeco 7 Peaks Residences is ₹13,000 per sq.ft. However, buyers who deposit an initial ₹10 lakh Expression of Interest (EOI) amount can lock their price at ₹12,000 per sq.ft. Unlike many developers, Eldeco is not charging separate parking or club membership fees over and above the base price; only PLC (Preferential Location Charges) and GST are applicable as per unit selection Based on previous Eldeco launches, PLC typically ranges between ₹400 to ₹800 per sq.ft, taking the expected all-inclusive price range to approximately ₹13,000 – ₹13,450 per sq.ft depending on tower and floor preference</p>\n",
      "highlights": "Exclusive 7 standalone towers spread over 7.5 acres with green views;\r\n4 side open towers with diagonal positioning for optimal airflow;\r\nEach apartment having 3 side open with infinite views;\r\nWraparound curved balconies and sunlit interiors in every apartment;\r\nAll apartments face greens or central tropical water features;\r\nSwimming Pool Deck;\r\n4 Swimming pools – Lap pool, tropical pool, all-weather heated pool and kids’ pool with sand beach;\r\nLavish clubhouse with state-of-the-art amenities",
      "location_advantages": "<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed\">Seamless access to Noida-Greater Noida Expressway &amp; Yamuna Expressway</span></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed\">close to the upcoming Noida International Airport</span></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed\">Near Delta 1 Metro Station (Aqua Line)</span></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed\">Close to industrial corridors like Ecotech and Kasna Industrial Area.</span></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed\">Radisson Blu Hotel 4.5 Km</span></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed\">Jaypee Cricket Stadium 17.3 Km</span></div>\n",
