      "faq_1_question": "Where is Eldeco 7 Peaks located?",
      "faq_1_answer": "Eldeco 7 Peaks Residences is located in Omicron 1A, Greater Noida, near Pari Chowk and connected via a 130-meter wide road. The project enjoys excellent connectivity and open green frontage, making it one of the most strategically positioned developments",
      "faq_2_question": "What configurations are available in Eldeco 7 Peaks?",
      "faq_2_answer": "Eldeco 7 Peaks offers premium 3 BHK + 3T residences in multiple layout variants and a 4 BHK + servant configuration. The project also features limited duplex penthouses on the top floors.",
      "faq_3_question": "What is the starting price of Eldeco 7 Peaks?",
      "faq_3_answer": "The basic sale price of Eldeco 7 Peaks starts at approximately ₹13,000 per sq. ft., with early booking benefits allowing buyers to lock in pricing at ₹12,000 per sq. ft. (subject to builder terms, PLC, and GST)",
      "faq_4_question": "Is Eldeco 7 Peaks a good investment in Greater Noida?",
      "faq_4_answer": "Yes, Eldeco 7 Peaks is considered a strong investment opportunity due to: Prime location in Omicron 1A Wide 130-meter road frontage Established residential ecosystem Branded developer track record Balanced end-user and investor demand The project’s",
      "faq_5_question": "What makes Eldeco 7 Peaks different from other projects in Greater Noida?",
      "faq_5_answer": "Eldeco 7 Peaks stands out because: Towers are diagonally placed for better sunlight and ventilation Almost 500 meters of open green buffer in front Only 4 apartments per floor Large curved balconies Low-density planning across 7.37 acres This design",
